---
title: Cannellini Bean & Roast Veggie Stew with Plant-Based Pesto & Garlic Flatbreads
description: We’ve thought about it and finally decided that we can’t keep this one all to ourselves any longer. Beans and roasted veggies soaking in a tomato herby stew is just too good to keep quiet about. Let’s all share this special stew together!
